{"tid":718682,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"非三大 辛苦捱到大學出黎竟然都係...","createTime":"2018-06-27T01:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T04:28:34.000Z","uid":134748,"like":29,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"92dc905a5716c493691b378b9c24dcff380cac8d","tid":718682,"uid":134748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:35:27.000Z","msg":"話說自己做緊既工種雖然要求語文係高啲，但都要一定既專業知識先做到。自問英文普通，雖然未係好好但一路都增值緊，對自己門專業都係。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩做夠一年，公司竟然請左個港大九唔搭八科既門外漢（不過佢有相關工作經驗）黎返工，一黎要仲要懶勤力搶走哂我手頭上啲野黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明自己語文能力唔高都冇得怨人，但我有既專業知識一定比佢多，有時好多野佢搶左黎做又要黎問番我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仆佢個街高招到丫，我唔係唔忍心見自己跟咁耐個既project 搞到一pat 屎咁我都廢撚事答佢<br />\n<br />\n唉，一句講哂，識英文等於大哂，就係有班白痴既老闆咁諗所以先搞到讀唔同專科非三大語文既學生一文不值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ee68d6325ce5bf043866bbd15af54ac9ba4175","tid":718682,"uid":130897,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"cafc1a1da7675aa9d14663c4e6402503b07694d7","tid":718682,"uid":170595,"like":43,"dislike":4,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"廢就廢啦講咁撚多"},{"pid":"a0fe3414923c28d204b6d21ed993a08ab55baf44","tid":718682,"uid":55991,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:38:06.000Z","msg":"咁無辦法<br />\n好多時同一個post<br />\n三大同八大，甚至非八大開個offer都會唔同<br />\n唯有經驗搭救"},{"pid":"7bff63ae6a0c456e64ef942f6c433d0e6487a1f9","tid":718682,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"master洗底囉<br />\n可以點?"},{"pid":"a022629a8d878eee5c86d7e1202c0a69a88a7448","tid":718682,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T01:50:26.000Z"